---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---
<BaseLayout title="Contact">
  <main class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-semibold">Contact</h1>

    <p class="mt-4 text-base leading-7 text-neutral-700 dark:text-neutral-300">
      I am open to thoughtful conversations around engineering, AI systems,
      product-oriented work, and collaboration opportunities.
    </p>

    <p class="mt-4 text-base leading-7 text-neutral-700 dark:text-neutral-300">
      If you are reaching out regarding a role, collaboration, or something
      related to my writing or demos, feel free to get in touch.
    </p>

    <div class="mt-8 space-y-4">
      <p class="text-base text-neutral-700 dark:text-neutral-300">
        <span class="font-medium text-neutral-900 dark:text-neutral-100">Email:</span>
        <br />
        <a
          href="mailto:contact@jiteshgosar.com"
          class="underline underline-offset-4"
        >
          contact@jiteshgosar.com
        </a>
      </p>

      <p class="text-base text-neutral-700 dark:text-neutral-300">
        <span class="font-medium text-neutral-900 dark:text-neutral-100">LinkedIn:</span>
        <br />
        <a
          href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/jiteshgosar/"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noreferrer"
          class="underline underline-offset-4"
        >
          linkedin.com/in/jiteshgosar
        </a>
      </p>
    </div>

    <p class="mt-8 text-sm leading-6 text-neutral-500 dark:text-neutral-400">
      When writing, a short message with context is appreciated.
    </p>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
